          "reviewBody": "It's a huge campus, a CBSE school with all modern amenities for children . They imbibe education as well as religious and cultural knowledge as it is managed by Kanchi shankaracharya trust. The environment is quiet pleasant and neat as well. It houses two temples, veda Patasala, auditorium, play area for kids and a museum too in the same campus.",
